<br>
woven mandrake 2 mandrake roots (alchemy supply) 66 <br>
picnic basket (snack) woven mandrake, boning 76 <br>
<br>
(Boning is made in a forge... steel boning (stackable) small brick ore, file, flask water 41 )<br>
<br>
